data.description: 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home on a cul-de-sac street in the Sierra Morado. Home offers upgraded kitchen w/ staggered uppers, corian counter-tops, stainless appliances, custom tile back-splash, custom range hood w/ pot filler! Luxury vinyl plank flooring. Master is downstairs w/ 4 additional bedrooms upstairs. The loft was converted w/ french & barn doors, could be 5th bedroom. Formal dining has a custom barn-door & fireplace! Master bedroom has custom fireplace. Every bedroom has a walk-in closet & ceiling fan. Living room has custom built in. Solar water heater. NEW Goettl AC! Vivint smart home security. Owned solar on payment plan, 0$ transfer fee. Conveniently located between community pool and the schools with easy access to miles of jogging. Vail schoo
